title.rendered: TREND Terrific Trimmers Sparkle Border, 2 1/4″” x 39″” Panels, Blue, 10/Set

content.rendered:
Sparkling trims decorate classrooms and enhance learning environments. Pre-cut, scalloped borders add a touch of dazzling color. Color(s): Blue Sparkle; Height: 2 1/4″”; Length: 39 ft; Quantity: 12 per set.
Is Discontinued By Manufacturer ‏ : ‎ No
Product Dimensions ‏ : ‎ 0.13 x 2.38 x 41 inches; 1 Pounds
Date First Available ‏ : ‎ February 28, 2011
Manufacturer ‏ : ‎ Trend Micro Incorporated
ASIN ‏ : ‎ B009R5TQW2

Sparkle Terrific Trimmers? are pre-cut and scalloped, featuring brilliant color and dazzling pattern.
Pre-cut with scalloped border edges.
